  <steps>
    <step num="0">In a blender or food processor, combine coconut yogurt, lemon juice, vinegar, salt, and pepper. When creamy, add chopped garlic and oil. Blend again. </step>
    <step num="1">Seed and grate cucumber and wrap in towel. </step>
    <step num="2">Squeeze excess water out of cucumber. </step>
    <step num="3">Add cucumber to coconut yogurt dip, and stir to blend. </step>
    <step num="4">Cover and chill 2-3 hours. </step>
    <step num="5">Garnish with dill. </step>
    <step num="6">Serve with chips, crackers, or veggies. </step>
    <step num="7">Enjoy! </step>
